<h3 class="endpoint">
    PUT /api/v1/appointment_groups/:id
  </h3>
<p>Update and return an appointment group. If new_appointments are specified,
the response will return a new_appointments array (same format as
appointments array, see âList appointment groupsâ action).</p>
